        "content": "<p>I think we should change the @ token from a Keyword/Punctuation to an UpperIdent token for correct styling syntax highlighting. Just want to see what others think?</p>\n<h2>Current</h2>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/22008/n_FNTTDnRvsPB2bapasXfdWi/Screenshot-2023-11-24-at-08.07.19.png\">Screenshot-2023-11-24-at-08.07.19.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/22008/n_FNTTDnRvsPB2bapasXfdWi/Screenshot-2023-11-24-at-08.07.19.png\" title=\"Screenshot-2023-11-24-at-08.07.19.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/22008/n_FNTTDnRvsPB2bapasXfdWi/Screenshot-2023-11-24-at-08.07.19.png\"></a></div><h2>Proposed</h2>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/22008/-L-rojrQ_evRiWqo7SuHxrzg/Screenshot-2023-11-24-at-08.09.40.png\">Screenshot-2023-11-24-at-08.09.40.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/22008/-L-rojrQ_evRiWqo7SuHxrzg/Screenshot-2023-11-24-at-08.09.40.png\" title=\"Screenshot-2023-11-24-at-08.09.40.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/22008/-L-rojrQ_evRiWqo7SuHxrzg/Screenshot-2023-11-24-at-08.09.40.png\"></a></div>",
